desc: Nicci Lee Fit, A professional fitness model and a guru when it comes to work out planning and meal preparation. Her expertise is being a key player in the fitness scene, creating products and plans. Weather you're into ﻿weight loss, muscle gain, or ﻿nutrition, her training guides will get you the results.

layout.text: Are you tired of working out and never changing? Have you hired a coach and NOT seen any changes? Do you struggle to find time to block off for training? Or how about you don't know what to eat or think you have to starve or sacrifice foods you love for boring food that you could never eat long term?
